<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4607721>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Falcidens ryokuyomaruae sp. nov. (A) holotype, NSMT-Mo 78608, preserved condition; (B) paratype #8, NSMT-Mo 78616, specimen in life; (C) pedal shield of paratype #8; (D) radula of holotype. Scale bars: 1 mm for A; 0.5 mm for B; 200 µm for C; 100 µm for D." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4607721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4607723>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Falcidens ryokuyomaruae sp. nov. Sclerites of holotype. (A, B) peribuccal region; (C, D) in foregut region; (E, F) in anterior midgut sac region; (G–I) in posterior midgut sac region; (J) in prepallial region; (K, L) at posterior margin of pallial region; (M) inside of posterior margin of pallial region. Scale bar: 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4607723/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

